1052.name: AA Nicro 625B
1052.Applications:
AA Nicro 625B is developed for welding and cladding nickel-based alloys such as alloy 625 or similar materials. This alloy can also be used for welding dissimilar nickel-based alloys to each other, to 
alloyed steels or to stainless steels and for joining 6% molybdenum super austenitic steels.
